<h3>Infrastructure</h3>

<p>ITMI is equipped with or has access to the best technical infrastructure in the country. Our channels’ studios are state-of-the-art and our trainees have access to them through internships, workshops and visits. Our own studio has cameras and edit machines for training purposes, but all the equipment is industry-standard—whether it is our cameras, the PCR, edit consoles, news software, audio equipment, or other applications.</p>
<p>
Our academic infrastructure includes a "Cybrary"-our online and offline resource centre that has a large collection of books, magazines, and thousands of online journals. All our classrooms are audiovisual-capable.</p>

<p>
India Today’s cafeterias down the road offer wholesome and hygienic food. Coffee and tea are available in our kitchen.</p>


<br>
<br>

<h3>Housing </h3>

<p>While ITMI does not have on-campus residence, several local guest houses are available separately for men and women all over Noida, and ITMI can recommend you accordingly to one and also guide you in the process.  </p>

<p>We will recommend you on our best insights of the following factors:</p>

<ol class="bottom-gap">
<li>-Proximity of markets, availability of groceries and public transport nearby</li>
<li>-Security—we prefer gated communities</li>
<li>-Hygienic food and environment</li>
<li>-Comfortable beds, television, storage, etc</li>
<li>-Optional facilities like air-conditioning, air-cooling, etc. (These are usually charged extra.)</li>
<li>-Negotiated rent for ITMI students. Normal monthly rent in Noida with the above amenities ranges between Rs 7,000 and Rs 10,000 for shared accommodation.</li>

</ol>
<br>
<p><em>For details, contact the Administration Department.</em></p>
<br>
<h3>Transport</h3>
<p>
ITMI provides transport free of charge from its Sector 57, Noida, campus to Noida City Centre Metro Station via the hostels. Metro rail service is available every few minutes from that station to various parts of Noida, Delhi and New Delhi. The shuttle is available in the morning and evening.</p>
      
